== Vector Dot Product

$
accent(a, arrow) dot accent(b, arrow) = vec(a_1, a_2, dots.v, a_n) dot vec(b_1, b_2, dots.v, b_n) = a_1 b_1 + a_2 b_2 + dots + a_n b_n
$

=== Magnitude (Length)

$
||accent(a, arrow)|| = sqrt(a_1^2 + a_2^2 + dots + a_n^2)
$

